Efficiency always come at the cost of resiliency. Higher ups want real time data which in turn result in needing the computers interconnected. But have a bigger problem. RuPay CC on UPI is very difficult to use. It will work only if the accepting party is registered as a business account/merchant. In close to 90% of the cases, the shops, businesses, cabs, vendors, all use a personal bank account linked to an individual. Hence UPI CC won't work on them, you will end up making P2P transaction from your bank account to a business instead of a P2M transaction.
